data.description: This amazing home has everything you have been looking for! Located in desirable Woodcreek neighborhood in Fate, this home features 4 bedrooms, 2 and half bathrooms, 3 living areas and 1 dining area. It has luxury vinyl plank flooring through out, inviting kitchen that has custom cabinets, granite counter tops, gas cooktop, walk in pantry and opens to the breakfast area and living room. The primary bedroom has luxury vinyl plank flooring and the primary bathroom has dual sinks, walk in closet and a huge shower with a sitting bench. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, game room, balcony and an incredible media room with built in 5.1 surround sound speakers and subwoofer. Outside has a covered patio and a nice grass backyard!
